videos.description: Aliyah Boston's triple double (16 points, 11 rebounds and 10 blocks) and Zia Cooke's 16-point night lift No. 4 South Carolina to a 62-50 win over No. 22 Georgia.
videos.headline: Boston, Cooke duo keep Gamecocks rolling
